                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.252/63a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-09-28T12:00:00-05:00"
                            >September 28, 1931—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>45. Your 119, September 25, 6 p.m. Approved, although the Department would prefer
                    30 days notice of termination instead of 15. Accept the latter if unable to
                    obtain the 30 days, which is the usual period in agreements of this kind.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
